      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783668358546,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  KPI cards: colour-coded left border per pillar, mono-set numeric value, up/down delta with colour meaning (green=good, red=needs attention)\n•  Bar chart compares monthly CO₂e against the active environmental goal target line\n•  Alerts ranked by risk (red=high, amber=medium) each with owner module and due date; click-through to the Compliance Issue record\n•  Department ranking table sortable by any score column; rank badge highlights top performer\n•  Leaderboard pulls live XP totals from Challenge Participation; avatar + department shown per employee\n•  “View report / See all” links on every panel deep-link to the corresponding List View, filtered",
      "fontSize": 11.6,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 83,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  KPI cards: colour-coded left border per pillar, mono-set numeric value, up/down delta with colour meaning (green=good, red=needs attention)\n•  Bar chart compares monthly CO₂e against the active environmental goal target line\n•  Alerts ranked by risk (red=high, amber=medium) each with owner module and due date; click-through to the Compliance Issue record\n•  Department ranking table sortable by any score column; rank badge highlights top performer\n•  Leaderboard pulls live XP totals from Challenge Participation; avatar + department shown per employee\n•  “View report / See all” links on every panel deep-link to the corresponding List View, filtered",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b0p8",
      "autoResize": true
    },
