    {
      "id": "fktx01nhgaoimbvi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 2174,
      "width": 1860,
      "height": 101.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#33403a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 366820615,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 1687247281,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783505423201,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  Checkbox column enables bulk actions: archive, export selection, bulk status change\n•  Filter chips scope the Module field instantly; “Filters” opens advanced criteria (date range, department, status, amount)\n•  “Group by” reorganizes rows into collapsible sections (e.g. by Department or Status)\n•  List / Kanban toggle (top right, not shown) renders the same filtered dataset as cards\n•  Status pill colour-codes lifecycle: Draft (grey) → Confirmed (green) → Validated (blue) → Needs review (red)\n•  Create opens a blank Form View record; Import/Export handle CSV/XLSX bulk operations\n•  Pagination footer shows selection count and “x–y / total” with prev/next controls",
      "fontSize": 11.6,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 97.5,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  Checkbox column enables bulk actions: archive, export selection, bulk status change\n•  Filter chips scope the Module field instantly; “Filters” opens advanced criteria (date range, department, status, amount)\n•  “Group by” reorganizes rows into collapsible sections (e.g. by Department or Status)\n•  List / Kanban toggle (top right, not shown) renders the same filtered dataset as cards\n•  Status pill colour-codes lifecycle: Draft (grey) → Confirmed (green) → Validated (blue) → Needs review (red)\n•  Create opens a blank Form View record; Import/Export handle CSV/XLSX bulk operations\n•  Pagination footer shows selection count and “x–y / total” with prev/next controls",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b2S8",
      "autoResize": true
    },
