      "versionNonce": 471229585,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783505417287,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  Status stepper shows workflow stage; Save re-validates the emission calculation and can advance state\n•  Smart buttons are clickable shortcuts into related records (Emission Factor, Attachments, Department Budget)\n•  Tabs separate core fields from calculation trace (Calculation Details) and linked source document\n•  Measured values render in monospace (tabular figures); descriptive fields render in the UI sans font\n•  Chatter logs both system events and user notes, supports @mentions and internal-only notes\n•  Discard reverts unsaved edits without leaving the record",
      "fontSize": 11.6,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 83,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  Status stepper shows workflow stage; Save re-validates the emission calculation and can advance state\n•  Smart buttons are clickable shortcuts into related records (Emission Factor, Attachments, Department Budget)\n•  Tabs separate core fields from calculation trace (Calculation Details) and linked source document\n•  Measured values render in monospace (tabular figures); descriptive fields render in the UI sans font\n•  Chatter logs both system events and user notes, supports @mentions and internal-only notes\n•  Discard reverts unsaved edits without leaving the record",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b3b8",
      "autoResize": true
    },
