      "versionNonce": 1264210815,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783505417287,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  Columns represent the challenge lifecycle: Draft → Active → Under Review → Completed; drag-and-drop moves cards\n•  Card shows pillar tag (Environmental / Social / Governance colour), XP reward and completion progress bar\n•  Avatar stack (not shown at this scale) lists enrolled participants with a “+N” overflow count\n•  Clicking a card opens the Challenge Form (title, description, XP, difficulty, evidence required, deadline)\n•  “Under Review” column feeds directly into the Admin Approvals queue for proof validation\n•  Completed cards trigger XP payout, Leaderboard refresh and Badge-unlock checks",
      "fontSize": 11.6,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 83,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  Columns represent the challenge lifecycle: Draft → Active → Under Review → Completed; drag-and-drop moves cards\n•  Card shows pillar tag (Environmental / Social / Governance colour), XP reward and completion progress bar\n•  Avatar stack (not shown at this scale) lists enrolled participants with a “+N” overflow count\n•  Clicking a card opens the Challenge Form (title, description, XP, difficulty, evidence required, deadline)\n•  “Under Review” column feeds directly into the Admin Approvals queue for proof validation\n•  Completed cards trigger XP payout, Leaderboard refresh and Badge-unlock checks",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b4WG",
      "autoResize": true
    },
