      "versionNonce": 2042698751,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783505417288,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  KPI Card — accent border, mono value, delta indicator; used on every dashboard and department scorecard\n•  Status Pill — colour-coded lifecycle/risk state; used in list rows, form ribbons and kanban cards\n•  Smart Button — clickable stat that drills into a related record; used across all Form Views\n•  Chatter Panel — log note + activity feed; attached to every record form (transactions, audits, policies, challenges)\n•  Filter Chip — quick single-field filter with an “active” state; used on every List View toolbar\n•  Rank Badge — numbered square marking table position; used in rankings and leaderboards\n•  Progress Bar — track + fill, used for goal progress, challenge completion and policy acknowledgement rate\n•  Avatar / Avatar Stack — circular initials, overflow “+N”; used in leaderboard, chatter and kanban cards\n•  Stepper / Ribbon — horizontal workflow stage indicator on record forms (Draft → Confirmed → Validated → Posted)\n•  Pagination Footer — selection count + “x–y / total” with prev/next; used on every List View",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 146,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  KPI Card — accent border, mono value, delta indicator; used on every dashboard and department scorecard\n•  Status Pill — colour-coded lifecycle/risk state; used in list rows, form ribbons and kanban cards\n•  Smart Button — clickable stat that drills into a related record; used across all Form Views\n•  Chatter Panel — log note + activity feed; attached to every record form (transactions, audits, policies, challenges)\n•  Filter Chip — quick single-field filter with an “active” state; used on every List View toolbar\n•  Rank Badge — numbered square marking table position; used in rankings and leaderboards\n•  Progress Bar — track + fill, used for goal progress, challenge completion and policy acknowledgement rate\n•  Avatar / Avatar Stack — circular initials, overflow “+N”; used in leaderboard, chatter and kanban cards\n•  Stepper / Ribbon — horizontal workflow stage indicator on record forms (Draft → Confirmed → Validated → Posted)\n•  Pagination Footer — selection count + “x–y / total” with prev/next; used on every List View",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b51",
      "autoResize": true
    },
